projects.name: STEGANOGRAPHY APPLICATION
projects.description: Designed and implemented a steganography application as part of a cryptography course project,enabling secure communication by concealing information within digital media. Implemented encryption and decryption functionalities to embed and extract messages securely within images.

projects.name: Mental Healthcare Facility Integrated with a Chatbot
projects.description: Developed a mental health chatbot using Botpress and Django to provide mental health support and assistance. Integrated a user-friendly interface for real-time interaction and personalized suggestions, enhancing user experience.

projects.name: DECENTRALIZED TOKEN EXCHANGER
projects.description: Developed a decentralized Token Exchanger, I spearheaded the creation of a groundbreaking platform. It is aimed at seamlessly converting native tokens and faucet tokens.

experiences.description: Specialized in enhancing drone security through work on lightweight ciphers as a research intern. Developed expertise in cryptographic algorithms. Implemented and optimized lightweight ciphers to fortify drone communication against potential threats. Strengthened problem-solving skills and adaptability. Gained hands-on experience in cybersecurity for unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs).
